---
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
import UserCheckbox from "../icons/UserCeck.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import imagenAbout from "../assets/imagen-about.jpg";
---

<div id="about">
  <SectionTitle id="about" title="Sobre mi" icon={UserCheckbox} />
  <section>
    <article>
      <p>
        Soy <strong>Ricardo</strong>, también conocido como <strong>Glutix</strong>.
        Mi camino en la programación comenzó en la universidad, y desde entonces
        descubrí en el <strong>desarrollo web y de software</strong> una forma de
        expresar mi creatividad y resolver problemas.
      </p>
      <p>
        A lo largo de este recorrido participé en proyectos colaborativos y
        personales que me ayudaron a crecer, no solo en lo técnico, sino también
        en lo <strong>humano</strong>: aprendí el valor del trabajo en equipo,
        la constancia y la búsqueda de soluciones simples para desafíos complejos.
      </p>
      <p>
        Hoy sigo explorando nuevas ideas y tecnologías, con el objetivo de
        <strong>crear aplicaciones útiles e innovadoras</strong> que generen un
        impacto positivo, mientras continúo creciendo tanto en lo <strong>profesional</strong>
        como en lo <strong>personal</strong>.
      </p>
    </article>

    <!-- Image wrapped to add the same effects as the header -->
    <div class="image-wrapper">
      <!-- Glow behind the image -->
      <div class="glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <Image class="image" src={imagenAbout} alt="imagen acerca de mi" />

      <!-- Scanlines overlay -->
      <div class="scanlines" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Accent tint -->
      <div class="tint" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Only 2 corners to not overcrowd the rotated image -->
      <span class="corner tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="corner br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;

    article {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;

      p {
        color: var(--text-normal);
        text-wrap: pretty;
        padding-right: 1rem;
      }

      strong {
        color: var(--text-enfasis);
      }
    }
  }

  /* ── Image wrapper — same pattern as header ──────────────── */
  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    /* Preserve the original rotation */
    transform: rotate(4deg);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    /* Size matches original image */
    width: 320px;
    height: 430px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    
    
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover {
    transform: rotate(2deg) translateY(-4px);
    
  }

  /* Glow — same recipe as header, behind everything */
  .glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    z-index: 0;
    box-shadow:
      0 22px 55px rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.28),
      0 8px 20px  rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.12),
      0 -4px 16px rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.05);
    transition: box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    height: fit-content;
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover .glow {
    box-shadow:
      0 32px 80px rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.42),
      0 12px 30px rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.22),
      0 -6px 20px rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.08);
  }

  /* Original image styles preserved, transform moved to wrapper */
  .image {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 320px;
    height: 430px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 24px var(--image-shadow));
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
    
    
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover .image {
    filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 32px var(--image-shadow));
  }

  /* Scanlines — same as header, fades on hover */
  .scanlines {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    border-radius: 16px;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 2px,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10) 2px,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.10) 4px
    );
    opacity: 1;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    height: fit-content;
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover .scanlines {
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  /* Accent tint top-left */
  .tint {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    border-radius: 16px;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(240, 228, 128, 0.07) 0%,
      transparent 55%
    );
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    height: fit-content;
  }

  /* Corners — expand on hover like in header */
  .corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-color: var(--text-enfasis);
    border-style: solid;
    opacity: 0.6;
    z-index: 3;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease, width 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .corner.tl { top: 8px;    left: 8px;  border-width: 2px 0 0 2px; }
  .corner.br { bottom: 8px; right: 8px; border-width: 0 2px 2px 0; }

  .image-wrapper:hover .corner {
    opacity: 1;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 950px) {
    section {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .image-wrapper {
      margin: 0 auto;
      transform: rotate(0deg);
      width: 300px;
      height: 350px;
    }

    .image-wrapper:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .image {
      width: 300px;
      height: 350px;
    }
  }
</style>